[04/12/2018 06:02:14] <font color="#0000ff"></font>
[04/12/2018 06:02:14] <font color="#0000ff">(Aplausos)</font>
[04/12/2018 06:02:18] <font color="#ffff00">¡Qué detallazo!</font>
