[04/12/2018 06:06:33] <font color="#ff00ff">¡"Pipa", ven!</font>
[04/12/2018 06:06:38] <font color="#0000ff"></font>
[04/12/2018 06:06:38] <font color="#0000ff">(Música)</font>
[04/12/2018 06:06:43] <font color="#00ffff">¡Uno ahogándose!</font>
